ESSENCE' 1.0

letting  D be domain int(1..4)

find     M : matrix indexed by [D] of D
find     a : D 

such that 


    ((M[1]*a = 1) => (M[1]*a >= 0)), 
    ((M[2]*a = 2) => (M[2]*a >= 0)), 
    ((M[3]*a = 3) => (M[3]*a >= 0)), 
    ((M[4]*a = 4) => (M[4]*a >= 0)), 

    (M[1]*a - 1 <= 0),  
    (M[2]*a - 2 <= 0),  
    (M[3]*a - 3 <= 0),  
    (M[4]*a - 4 <= 0)
